437
00:31:27,124 --> 00:31:30,873
- Mr. Paley, Mr. Murrow is here.
- Thanks, Miss Mary.

438
00:31:31,462 --> 00:31:34,249
- Hello, Ed. - Bill...
- Sit over here, will you?

439
00:31:35,090 --> 00:31:36,169
