440
00:31:36,592 --> 00:31:38,999
- Your son?
- All well, thanks. How's Babe?

441
00:31:39,136 --> 00:31:42,303
She's fine. Her fundraiser
got rained on, so...

442
00:31:42,723 --> 00:31:45,593
- Oh! That's why I never plan
on anything. - Really?

443
00:31:47,144 --> 00:31:48,389
You'd never know.

444
00:31:52,274 --> 00:31:53,554
Reading fiction?

445
00:31:54,192 --> 00:31:56,066
I hope so. You tell me.

446
00:31:57,487 --> 00:31:59,314
Now we know
how they're gonna come at us.

447
00:31:59,406 --> 00:32:02,323
That's just the first shot.
Somebody's going to go down.

448
00:32:02,409 --> 00:32:05,030
Have you checked your facts?
Are you on safe ground?

449
00:32:07,330 --> 00:32:10,201
- Bill, it's time. Show our cards.
- My cards.

450
00:32:11,042 --> 00:32:14,956
You lose, what happens?
5 guys find themselves out of work.

451
00:32:15,380 --> 00:32:19,591
I'm responsible for a lot more
than 5 goddamn reporters. Let it go.

452
00:32:21,344 --> 00:32:23,502
McCarthy will self-destruct,
Cohn, all of them.

453
00:32:23,596 --> 00:32:26,051
You said Corporate
would not interfere with Editorial...

454
00:32:26,140 --> 00:32:27,634
...and that the News
was to be left...

455
00:32:27,725 --> 00:32:29,516
We don't make the news,
we report the news.

456
00:32:29,602 --> 00:32:32,353
He's marked as Communists.

457
00:32:32,438 --> 00:32:34,477
If he goes too far,
the Senate will investigate him...

458
